<section id="building-my-first-image-classifier" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="building-my-first-image-classifier">Building My First Image Classifier</h2>
<p>Diving into computer vision with FastAI has been an incredible learning experience. Here‚Äôs what I‚Äôve discovered while building my first image classifier.</p>
