<section id="key-insights" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="key-insights">Key Insights</h2>
<p><strong>Transfer Learning</strong> - Pre-trained models like ResNet dramatically improve results with limited data.</p>
<p><strong>Data Augmentation</strong> - Simple transformations boost model generalization significantly.</p>
<p><strong>Learning Rate</strong> - FastAI‚Äôs learning rate finder is a game-changer for optimization.</p>
</section>
<section id="real-application" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="real-application">Real Application</h2>
<p>I applied these concepts to my <a href="https://github.com/adilsiraju/Architecture-Style-Classifier/">Architectural Style Classifier</a>, achieving <strong>73% accuracy</strong> across 25 architectural styles through:</p>
<ul>
<li>Quality data curation</li>
<li>Appropriate augmentation for architectural images<br>
</li>
<li>Smart fine-tuning strategy</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="next-steps" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="next-steps">Next Steps</h2>
<ul>
<li>Advanced augmentation techniques</li>
<li>Model interpretation with GradCAM</li>
<li>Production deployment strategies</li>
<li>Multi-label classification</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="resources" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="resources">Resources</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://course.fast.ai/">FastAI Course</a> - Practical deep learning</li>
<li><a href="https://paperswithcode.com/">Papers with Code</a> - Latest research</li>
<li><a href="https://www.kaggle.com/datasets">Kaggle</a> - Quality datasets</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p>The FastAI course continues to amaze with its practical approach. More updates coming as I progress!</p>


